snippet.title: Merc Docs
snippet.description:
Hi,
welcome to Merc Docs. We make Mystery, True Crime, Horror, Space, Facts and Short documentary videos. We try to make at least one video every week but sometimes you know life happens xD  If you enjoy our content, please subscribe! :)


1000 subscribers reached: 1 September 2016
10,000 subscribers reached: 13 December 2016
50,000 subscribers reached: 26 March 2018
100,000 Subscribers reached: 9 January 2019

Follow Merc Doc on
Twitter:https://twitter.com/07Merc
Facebook:http://goo.gl/ncD8Sv

For business inquiries: 07mercc@gmail.com
